# Compiled GResource bundles are build outputs — ignored by pattern, not by
# one hardcoded path (a hardcoded path is how a stale src/ui/folio.gresource
# survived the src/ui -> src/giruntime/ui move and got committed).
*.gresource
folio.pyz

__pycache__/

